有弄明白或難以理解的事物：這事直到現在還是一個謎。謎團。<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AC%8E%E5%BA%95\" class=\"sword\">謎底</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-mi2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">mí</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-di3.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone3\">dǐ</a> ]: answer to a riddle<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AC%8E%E8%AA%9E\" class=\"sword\">謎語</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-mi2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">mí</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-yu3.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone3\">yǔ</a> ]: riddle; conundrum; Classifiers: <a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details/?word=%E6%9D%A1\">条</a><br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AC%8E%E5%9C%98\" class=\"sword\">謎團</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-mi2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">mí</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-tuan2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">tuán</a> ]: riddle; enigma; unpredictable situation; elusive matters</span>\n<hr>\n<div>\n  <div>\n    <div><span class=\"tc\">(Simplified: 谜)</span></div>\n    <div><b>Ideographic</b>: Bewitching <a class=\"dictips\">迷</a> words <a class=\"dictips\">言</a>; <a class=\"dictips\">迷</a> also provides the pronunciation</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"line-height:1.6\">\n  <ul style=\"margin-left:-20px;margin-top:-10px\">\n    <li class=\"pt-2\"><b>Chinese Definition:</b></li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n<div>HSK: 6</div>\n<hr><span><span style=\"color:#1ce63d\">Kanshudo mnemonic:</span>the perplexing (<a href=\"/kanji/%E8%BF%B7\">迷</a>) words (<a href=\"/kanji/%E8%A8%80\">言</a>) are a riddle</span>\n<div>On-Yomi: <span class=\"japanese\" style=\"color:red\">メイ、ベイ</span></div>\n<div>Kun-Yomi: <span class=\"japanese\" style=\"color:#9ab5ff\">なぞ</span></div>\n<div><img src=\"E8AC8E.png\"></div>\n<div id=\"heisig_constituent\"><span style=\"color:tomato\">Heisig constituents</span>: riddle, say, words, keitai, mouth, astray, rice, road</div>\n<div><span style=\"color:tomato\">Heisig</span>: Words . . . astray.</div>\n<div><span style=\"color:tomato\">Chinese</span>: Words meant to make you feel lost are those of a riddle.</div>\n<hr><span><span style=\"color:tomato\">koohii1</span>: Words meant to lead you astray are those of a riddle.</span>\n<hr><span><span style=\"color:tomato\">koohii2</span>: I led Socrates astray with my riddle. He quit philosophizing and thought only about the riddle.</span>\n<hr>\n<div><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Meaning:</span> riddle<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Hanzi:</span> 谜<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Story:</span> A bunch of words that makes you feel really lost is a riddle.<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Kind:</span> traditional<br><img src=\"lf_35868.gif\"></div>\n<div>\n  <hr><span>Lesson: 26&nbsp;</span><span>frameNoV4: 2709&nbsp;</span><span>frameNoV6: 994&nbsp;</span><span>Strokes: 16&nbsp;</span><span>Jouyou Grade: JH&nbsp;</span>\n</div>\n<hr><span id=\"jp_example_words\">謎(なぞ): riddle, puzzle, enigma</span>\n<hr><img src=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/kangxiArchaic.php?hash=183a0396ba4c33ded37cdf442c3a618b\"><br>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"humanum_full_description\">從「 言 」從「 迷 」，「 迷 」亦聲。本義是隱語、謎語。《玉篇．言部》：「謎，隱言也。」《說文新附》：「謎，隱語也。从言、迷，迷亦聲。」如《文心雕龍．諧讔》：「自魏代已來，頗非俳優，而君子嘲隱，化為謎語。謎也者，迴互其辭，使昏迷也。」明代馮夢龍《警世通言．金令史美婢酬秀童》：「好兄弟，你須是眼見的實，莫又做猜謎的話！」 「 謎 」也比喻還沒有弄明白或難以理解的事物。如老舍《四世同堂》：「在思想上、言論上和一部分行動上，瑞宣簡直是她的一個永不可解的謎。」</div>\n  <div id=\"humanum_full_description_en\">From \" words\" to \" fans\", \" fans\" also sound. The original meaning is cryptic and riddle. \"Jade articles. Yan Bu: \"Mystery, hidden words.\" \"Shu Wen Xin Attached\": \"Riddles, hidden words. From words, fans, fans also sound.\" Such as \"Wen Xin Diao Long. Humor\": \"Since the Wei Dynasty has come, it is quite a haiyu, but the gentleman mocks and hides and turns into a riddle. The riddle also turns into a coma.\" Feng Menglong of the Ming Dynasty \"Jing Shi Tong Yan. \"Jin Lingshi, Maid's Maid Rewarding Xiu Tong\": \"Brother, you must be what you see. Don't try to guess again!\" \" Mystery\" is also a metaphor for things that have not been understood or are difficult to understand. For example, Lao She's \"Four Generations Under One Roof\": \"In terms of thought, speech, and some actions, Rui Xuan is simply an unsolvable mystery of her.\"</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"hanziyuan\">\n  <div class=\"etymology-nav\" id=\"&#x8B0E;\">\n    <div class=\"alert alert-success etymology-alert m-0\" role=\"alert\"></div>\n    <div class=\"row bg-info border-purple border-top mx-0 row-eq-height\" id=\"E04179\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-4 p-0\">\n        <div class=\"p-1\">\n          <p></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in your browser 繁体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x8B0E;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in Unicode standard 繁体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=8B0E\" target=\"_blank\">U+8B0E</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-8B0E\"></p>\n          <p><b>Older traditional characters 旧繁体字/异体字:</b> Not exist</p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in your browser 简体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x8C1C;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in Unicode standard 简体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=8C1C\" target=\"_blank\">U+8C1C</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-8C1C\"></p>\n          <p><b>Main pronunciation 主要发音:</b> m&#xED;</p>\n          <p><b>Other pronunciations 其它发音:</b> Not exists.</p>\n          <p><b>Original meaning 本义:</b> Meaning a riddle.</p>\n          <p><b>English senses 英语理解:</b> riddle, conundrum; puzzle</p>\n          <p><b>Usage example 用法举例:</b> &#x8B0E;&#x8A9E; m&#xED; y&#x1D4; (conumdrum)</p>\n          <p><b>Importance by frequency 常用频率:</b> 2684</p>\n          <p><b>Shuowen 说文解字:</b> &#x96B1;&#x8A9E;&#x4E5F;&#x5F9E;&#x8A00;&#x8FF7;&#x8FF7;&#x4EA6;&#x8072;</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Character 