iddles!</i></span><br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=謎\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=謎&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=謎\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=謎\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=謎\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/謎\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=謎\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/謎\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=謎&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#謎\">Char lookup site</a></p><br><span class=\"tiny\">Examples: <span class=\"japanese\">謎 (なぞ)</span></span>\n<div class=\"notes optional small\">込 (внутрь), 米 (рис), 言 (слово)</div>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"言","pinyins":["yan2","yan2"]},{"glyph":"迷","pinyins":["mi2"]}],"isMentionedAt__hanziyuan_without_charactersWithComponent":["谜"]}